{"tid":384311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港女仔唔夠主動？","createTime":"2017-09-02T08:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T08:45:18.000Z","uid":31901,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67bd0281201b13d1635a253b886ababf89afd354","tid":384311,"uid":31901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:01:49.000Z","msg":"感覺上香港女仔同大陸女仔相比<br />\n好多時都好被動 等人追<br />\n我睇身邊識嘅人 例如傾計咁<br />\n大陸女仔如果對對方有興趣 好多會主動搵人<br />\n而香港女仔就算鐘意對方 都唔主動whatsapp人<br />\n可能怕魚所以就寧願被動"},{"pid":"2e2f01ebe66f70e7edf23e9f6d5edd905bff5a77","tid":384311,"uid":69120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346480c1ccec5e3f7ed303c3bf65bedaa0bd6fdf","tid":384311,"uid":2719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:40:38.000Z","msg":"香港女洗乜主動<br />\n正係被動應付啲狗公都夠忙啦"},{"pid":"9044b9bf45ef2d14ae6723c3b8bada4a43f490a1","tid":384311,"uid":81684,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:42:08.000Z","msg":"對你啫<br />\n照吓塊閪鏡先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76cfa15ddb5793bfff9a614b53e342395bfca54","tid":384311,"uid":31901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港女洗乜主動<br />\n正係被動應付啲狗公都夠忙啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家玩法相同啫<br />\n狗公漁翁撒網同時搵幾條女<br />\n女神就同時拖著幾個男仔<br />\n好啲就可能係想睇定啲個男仔適唔適合自己<br />\n差啲就係騎牛搵馬<br />\n結果變成收兵"},{"pid":"77ec40a3dc53a150a292d5f8d5f9254694040ab2","tid":384311,"uid":31901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對你啫<br />\n照吓塊閪鏡先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}